question: Show fiction books and non-fiction books with a rating of 2.5.
sql_query1:
SELECT Books.Title 
FROM Books
WHERE (Books.Literature = "Fiction Book" OR Books.Literature = "Non-fiction Book") AND Books.Rating = 2.5
sql_query2:
SELECT Books.Title 
FROM Books
WHERE Books.Literature = "Fiction Book" OR Books.Literature = "Non-fiction Book" AND Books.Rating = 2.5
interpretation1: Which fiction books have a rating of 2.5 and which non-fiction books have the same rating?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all fiction books and also provide a list of non-fiction books with a rating of 2.5.
